metadata.name: ABCalm
metadata.description:
A - Not to cry
B - Be a responsible adult
C - Be calm and smile.

The power 
of the will
is nothing more than
a postgraduate degree
in self-love. 

We 
the defeated, 
A - we cry,
B - we rain.

We, 
the vanquished
C - we carry
(inside)
a river
that swims, 
but nothing.
